Description
-----------
This is a simple CardDAV-Client written in PHP called "CardDAV-PHP".


Features
--------
* query a CardDAV-Server with XML-Response (simplified or raw)
* supports many authentification methods
* add/update/delete vCards on a CardDAV-Server
* get single vCards (raw or extended xml) from a CardDAV-Server
* check CardDAV-Server connection
* tested CardDAV-Servers: DAViCal, Apple Addressbook Server, memotoo, SabreDAV, ownCloud


Installation
------------
* nothing to install - it's standalone
* requires curl since version 0.4
* documentation can be found in the class itself

